com.tangosol.run.xml
Class SimpleParser

java.lang.Object
  com.tangosol.util.Base
      com.tangosol.run.xml.SimpleParser

public class SimpleParser
extends Base

This class uses the XmlTokenizer to produce an XmlDocument from XML text.

1.00, 2001.07.16
Author:
Cameron Purdy
